  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description:</h2>Tackle the challenge of drawing hands with ease using the Lite version of HAELE 3D - Hand Poser. This essential tool provides a reliable hand reference whenever you need it. Overcome the complexity of hand illustrations with built-in hand poses, customizable poses, lights, and environment options with intuitive controls.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570230/extras/fcda8c346e67463cb7764f3b32a2f39d.poster.avif?t=1773168416\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570230/extras/fcda8c346e67463cb7764f3b32a2f39d.webm?t=1773168416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570230/extras/fcda8c346e67463cb7764f3b32a2f39d.mp4?t=1773168416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570230/extras/da440d438c1c6d042bd54865f782153a.poster.avif?t=1773168416\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570230/extras/da440d438c1c6d042bd54865f782153a.webm?t=1773168416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570230/extras/da440d438c1c6d042bd54865f782153a.mp4?t=1773168416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570230/extras/6f7a3d8529d88df862a007e23d5de7f7.poster.avif?t=1773168416\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570230/extras/6f7a3d8529d88df862a007e23d5de7f7.webm?t=1773168416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570230/extras/6f7a3d8529d88df862a007e23d5de7f7.mp4?t=1773168416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570230/extras/efe17270076b94ae8bdd7a4d6223fb3e.poster.avif?t=1773168416\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570230/extras/efe17270076b94ae8bdd7a4d6223fb3e.webm?t=1773168416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570230/extras/efe17270076b94ae8bdd7a4d6223fb3e.mp4?t=1773168416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570230/extras/0c28b0d510a83b31f862c9925f7b8a2a.poster.avif?t=1773168416\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570230/extras/0c28b0d510a83b31f862c9925f7b8a2a.webm?t=1773168416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570230/extras/0c28b0d510a83b31f862c9925f7b8a2a.mp4?t=1773168416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Male and Female Hand Morphs:</strong> Choose from a variety of hand morphs to suit your artistic vision.<br></li><li><strong>Preset Poses:</strong> Access a collection of ready-made hand poses for quick inspiration.<br></li><li><strong>Custom Posing:</strong> Craft your own unique hand poses tailored to your artistic requirements.<br></li><li><strong>Editable Lights:</strong> Control the atmosphere with adjustable lighting, including 1 Point light (color, intensity, transformation), Environment light (HDRI map, intensity), and Ground light (color, intensity).<br></li><li><strong>Environment Options: </strong>Select from HDRI studio backgrounds, solid background colors, toggle floor visibility, and customize floor color and reflectivity.<br></li><li><strong>Preset Skin Tones:</strong> Explore a range of predefined skin tones to enhance realism.<br></li><li><strong>Adjustable Camera Settings:</strong> Fine-tune camera angles, locations, positions, and field of view for the perfect reference.<br></li><li><strong>Save and Load Scenes:</strong> Save your setups for future use and load them at any time.<br></li><li><strong>Load Presets:</strong> Quickly access predefined configurations to streamline your workflow.</li></ul><br>HAELE 3D - Hand Poses Lite is an easy to use anatomy and gesture drawing reference tool designed for beginner to advanced artists. It serves as a resource for learning how to draw human hands. Whether your art style is realistic, stylized, cartoon, anime or anything in between this is easy to use app complements tutorials and aids practicing your hand drawing or sculpting skills  or sculpting from sketch to finish.",
